{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Complex Combat</h2>Interstellar warfare is more complex than larger numbers beating smaller ones. A commander must always consider the weapons of enemy systems, the strength of each side\u2019s probes in flight, and openings you may be creating for your opponent.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/ComplexCombat.gif?t=1725030021\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collecting Relics</h2>Each run is unique with hundreds of different relic combinations to experiment with from filling the skies with gunfire and mines, to creating elite attack squadrons capable of defeating 5 times their number in flight.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/Relics.gif?t=1725030021\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Beyond the Run</h2>Progression isn't limited to a single run as, at the end of every run, you will gain research which will unlock new relics for future runs, and each achievement you complete will unlock a modifier that you can activate to change some core part of future runs.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102650/extras/Research.gif?t=1725030021\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Explosive Retribution","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3102650/1e3fbe60bf3723c9476f944275257c24e99ec0ec.jpg"},{"name":"Friend of the Weak","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3102650/e4ad3c220fed1c121cb6b84f509ce95a63af7a95.jpg"},{"name":"Mk I Expertise","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3102650/9f1c397d881ef98413b6b048ba71755e3bebc656.jpg"},{"name":"Mk III Expertise","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3102650/aa9181ab55bace5745eef484aa8dcf82f8748a59.jpg"},{"name":"Mk V Expertise","pa